name: Takamichi style and cover (no trigger words version)
description:
Recommended generating at 640x896.

Trained at TF32 precision and saved as float. Still 128 dim size.

Use AOM2

Note: Feel free to see the metadata of my lora I included the full training cmdline if you wish to try and make it yourself.

modelVersions.name: REAL V1 AOM2
modelVersions.description:
Well it's really 1 Epoch but 27 repeats.
Dataset used all Takamichi's Comic LO covers numbering 229.

Trained on AOM2 hardcore as that was the most popular.

This was a test train. But it turned out quite well.
Edit: I guess civitai does not save file names when you upload it. The file was supposed to be called CoLOv5t_fp32.safetensors as shown in the example images.
